now, hasn't it, navigator?

515
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:31,063
We reached Little Garden
without so much as seeing Mr. 3

516
00:20:31,096 --> 00:20:33,131
‐‐[thudding continues]
‐‐while on our way here.

517
00:20:33,165 --> 00:20:36,335
Now to me that seems to
indicate that you fools

518
00:20:36,401 --> 00:20:38,770
missed Mr. 3's ship entirely.

519
00:20:38,804 --> 00:20:40,272
No, sir. That can't be true!

520
00:20:40,305 --> 00:20:41,506
[MR. 2]
Hmm.

521
00:20:41,573 --> 00:20:43,842
It sort of sounds like you're
questioning my intelligence.

522
00:20:43,909 --> 00:20:44,943
Not at all, sir.

523
00:20:44,977 --> 00:20:46,345
Be quiet, you.

524
00:20:46,411 --> 00:20:49,681
All we have to do is
kill the pathetic Mr. 3.

525
00:20:49,748 --> 00:20:50,983
It should be an easy mission

526
00:20:51,016 --> 00:20:53,952
and one at which we have
no excuse to fail.

527
00:20:53,952 --> 00:20:55,954
We must complete
the mission soon.

528
00:20:55,954 --> 00:20:58,357
If we don't, then Mr. 1 and
his partner will be sent out

529
00:20:58,423 --> 00:21:01,093
to make sure I end up dead.

530
00:21:01,126 --> 00:21:01,927
‐‐Clear enough for you?!

531
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:03,262
‐‐[MEN gasp]
‐‐Clear enough for you?!

532
00:21:03,295 --> 00:21:04,963
Now if you don't
want to answer to me,

533
00:21:04,963 --> 00:21:06,698
then you'd better get to work‐‐

534
00:21:06,765 --> 00:21:09,768
lookin' for that Mr. 3.

535
00:21:09,801 --> 00:21:13,438
I want this ship going as fast
as it can, you imbeciles!

536
00:21:13,472 --> 00:21:16,375
We're heading to
Alabasta immediately!

537
00:21:16,441 --> 00:21:19,878
[MEN] Yes, sir, Mr. 2,
Mr. Bon Clay, sir!

538
00:21:20,979 --> 00:21:21,980
[CROCODILE]
What's this?

539
00:21:22,014 --> 00:21:25,651
Pirates are attacking
towns inside the kingdom?

540
00:21:25,684 --> 00:21:28,687
Don't they know this country
is protected by Crocodile?

541
00:21:28,720 --> 00:21:31,390
[MISS ALL SUNDAY] Who can
tell what they're thinking.

542
00:21:31,456 --> 00:21:33,892
A country where riots
are constantly brewing

543
00:21:33,959 --> 00:21:36,161
may be considered
an easy target.

544
00:21:36,194 --> 00:21:38,397
[footsteps]

545
00:21:38,463 --> 00:21:40,899
You'll go?

546
00:21:40,966 --> 00:21:41,967
[CROCODILE]
Naturally.

547
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:44,903
I do have a public
duty to uphold.

548
00:21:44,970 --> 00:21:47,673
[MISS ALL SUNDAY]
How very kind of you, sir.

549
00:21:49,741 --> 00:21:51,076
Yes, I'm a kind man.

550
00:21:51,143 --> 00:21:53,478
We Warlords are charged
with protecting the public

551
00:21:53,512 --> 00:21:55,080
from pirate threats.

552
00:21:55,147 --> 00:21:57,716
We are heroes to
these people, after all.

553
00:21:57,749 --> 00:21:58,984
[CROCODILE chuckles]

554
00:22:07,359 --> 00:22:09,895
<i>♪My life has been too still</i>

555
00:22:09,928 --> 00:22:12,364
<i>My heart is unfulfilled</i>

556
00:22:12,397 --> 00:22:17,002
<i>But you could be</i>
<i>the one to set me free.</i>

557
00:22:17,936 --> 00:22:20,272
<i>Something has to change</i>

558
00:22:20,339 --> 00:22:22,708
<i>My world can rearrange</i>

559
00:22:22,741 --> 00:22:28,880
<i>I'll do anything as long</i>
<i>as you are with me!</i>

560
00:22:28,880 --> 00:22:33,752
<i>I've grown stronger</i>
<i>having you by my side</i>

561
00:22:33,785 --> 00:22:39,124
<i>We've started on</i>
<i>an everlasting ride</i>

562
00:22:39,191 --> 00:22:44,229
<i>I'm invincible when</i>
<i>your love is near</i>

563
00:22:44,229 --> 00:22:49,534
<i>When I'm with you</i>
<i>I have no fear!</i>

564
00:22:49,568 --> 00:22:52,771
<i>Let's see how far</i>

565
00:22:52,804 --> 00:22:54,773
<i>We can make this go!</i>

566
00:22:54,806 --> 00:22:58,043
<i>The world is ours</i>

567
00:22:58,076 --> 00:22:59,911
<i>Future's bright, I know!</i>

568
00:22:59,945 --> 00:23:03,081
<i>I see it shine</i>

569
00:23:03,081 --> 00:23:08,253
<i>In the distance, glistening</i>
<i>like water when the sun</i>

570
00:23:08,253 --> 00:23:11,423
<i>Rises in the dawn!♪</i>

571
00:23:17,129 --> 00:23:18,930
