574
00:23:21,933 --> 00:23:23,435
[ZORO] What kind of
useless chef are you?!

575
00:23:23,435 --> 00:23:25,170
[SANJI] Hey, you want me
to kick you in the face?

576
00:23:25,237 --> 00:23:26,071
[LUFFY]
Shut up, guys!

577
00:23:26,104 --> 00:23:27,406
[SANJI, ZORO]
This is all your fault!

578
00:23:27,439 --> 00:23:29,274
[NAMI]
Look! We can see the island now!

579
00:23:29,274 --> 00:23:31,176
[LUFFY] All right then.
We'll land and eat!

580
00:23:31,243 --> 00:23:32,177
Oh, and help Vivi.

581
00:23:32,244 --> 00:23:33,979
